<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[ض]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[الأُبْض]</span>: الدهر بالضاد معجمة، والجمع آباضٌ،<span class="c5"> قال:</span> <span class="c2">«١»</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>في حِقْبَةٍ عِشْنَا بِذَاكَ أُبْضا<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>... و <span class="c4">[فُعْلَة]</span> بالهاء<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
